{"tid":551914,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（無圖）異國情風乘車記","createTime":"2018-02-06T05:26:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T05:37:20.000Z","uid":124985,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d01dd2196fa098a570cfc9092d39fbf84d75f033","tid":551914,"uid":124985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T05:26:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/06/130448_14c021c7450ead6051ccd41881ce1539.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F06%2F130448_14c021c7450ead6051ccd41881ce1539.jpg&h=e802c578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搭搭下車 突然有四位異國妙齡少女上車 拎住個大喇叭係到大大聲播歌 嘈醒左好多乘客 仲係到扭腰跳舞 各種自拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有個女士係佢地身邊啤足全程 最後大罵一句 「你地班垃圾！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地都不甘示弱 講左句「你食屎啦！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正評：支持女士 嘈到咁 屌得啱<br />\n負評：香港國際社會 包容各種文化同聲音"},{"pid":"138c78a144e31b7a080e3a43704131ff987f2155","tid":551914,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T05:28:43.000Z","msg":"正評： 樓主死全家。<br />\n負評： 樓主全家死。<br />\n<br />\non99 投票撚"},{"pid":"709b0af6d1e6cb48691221114a81685052df2f12","tid":551914,"uid":124985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T05:29:08.000Z","msg":"Btw 真心幾索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b596a57634c439b19c9b97db1cde9e683d33bd","tid":551914,"uid":124985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T05:30:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正評： 樓主死全家。<br />\n負評： 樓主全家死。<br />\n<br />\non99 投票撚</blockquote><br />\nSorry 囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好惡呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3aa13621282898c6a09b258e3165979811373f7","tid":551914,"uid":124985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim